item.title: 10/4 4-5p FLY Art Center volunteer orientation, FLY Creativity Lab, Ypsilanti
item.description: Christine Bruxvoort sent me these details on the FLY Art Center's upcoming volunteer orientation. When the volunteer orientation is going to be: Oct 4, 2014 4:00 p.m. - 5:00 p.m. Where it's going to be: FLY Creativity Lab, 40 N. Huron, Ypsilanti, 48197 (between Michigan and Pearl). Contact: Chris at 734-217-2228 or info@flyartcenter.org. Who is invited: Any interested adult or teen. Come to find out what we are about or sign up that night on our volunteer list.
